    "description": "A deterministic flow to determine if customer has enough money to make a wire transfer. If they do have enough, the flow checks to see if the amount is less than $10,000. If it is, flow will initiate the wire transfer. If it's more than $10,000, the flow returns a message telling the agent the customer needs to call a specialist.",
